- Primary Hover: rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.2) - Hover backgrounds
- Secondary: #3B82F6 (blue-500) - Secondary accents
- Success: #10B981 (emerald-500)
- Error: #EF4444 (red-500)
- Warning: #F59E0B (amber-500)

### Background Colors
- Gradient: from-[#0a0e27] via-[#1a1f3a] to-[#252d47]
- Surface: #1a1f3a (cards, modals)
- Surface Hover: #252d47

### Text Colors
- Primary: text-white
- Secondary: text-gray-300
- Muted: text-gray-400
- Accent: text-cyan-400

### Border Colors
- Default: border-slate-700/60
- Hover: border-cyan-400/50

